<html>
    <head>
        <title>
            Text tranform and text decoration
        </title>
        <style>
            h1{
                text-decoration:underline;
                text-transform:uppercase
            }
            p{
                text-transform:none;
                text-decoration:overline;
            }
            h2{
                text-decoration:line-through;
                text-transform:lowercase;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>
            Text transform and text decoration
        </h1>
        <p>
            In CSS, text transform and decoration are controlled using the text-transform and text-decoration properties, respectively. These properties allow you to change the case of text and add or style decorative lines. 
        </p>
        <h2>
            Codingal
        </h2>
    </body>
</html>
